title: Spanish Garlic Shrimp (Gambas al Ajillo) - Food Wishes
description:
Learn how to make a Spanish Garlic Shrimp recipe! I pretty much love any and all recipes from Spain, but this fast, easy garlic shrimp recipe, or gambas al ajillo, as it’s called over there, may be my all-time favorite. Visit https://foodwishes.blogspot.com/2018/06/spanish-garlic-shrimp-gambas-al-ajillo.html for the ingredients, more information, and many, many more video recipes. I hope you enjoy this amazing Spanish Garlic Shrimp recipe!

You can also find my content on Allrecipes: http://allrecipes.com/recipes/16791/everyday-cooking/special-collections/web-show-recipes/food-wishes/”
